        <updateDate>2020-03-23T15:11:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>This bill revises the methodology for apportioning federal highway funds among states to ensure that each state receives an aggregate apportionment equal to at least 100% of the estimated tax payments attributable to certain highway users in the state.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
